      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the refined interior to the flawless exterior finish, remains in showroom state. Mechanically uncompromised and meticulously maintained, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a truly pristine specimen of automotive engineering.",
