    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. It's in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one, and it really shows in every little detail. There isn't a single scratch or blemish to be found anywhere. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
