      "description": "Presenting a true time-capsule specimen. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-floor condition, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-finish luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather retains its factory-fresh scent and supple texture, with no evidence of bolster wear or UV fading. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014the engine bay is detailed to a concours standard, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Accompanied by a full suite of service records, the original window sticker, and all sets of keys, this is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
