      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride! This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014it seriously looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and professionally detailed. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or dent anywhere! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it for yourself!",
